# CLOCKWISE DIRECTION IN ORDER FOR BACK-FACE CULLING TO WORK
# FACE SYNTAX: v1, v2, v3, r, g, b
# (v1, v2, v3): Vertice ID for each Vertex in Polygon
# (r, g, b): Color value for face, will cap at 255
